body:
I often play customs to practise with my champs and I hate how there are only intermediate and beginner bots. This makes it very hard to practise jungling, as the bots can&#039;t jungle and/or are too easy to beat to simulate a real game. _Please, please, please_ can you work on introducing hard bots who can at least simulate the levels of a Bronze 5 player, because at the moment, bots are in Wood 5.
Thanks Riot. I hope to see this introduced soon.
{{champion:35}} {{summoner:14}}
